hopobject.body: Not in at the moment buylegalsteroids.tk Well, of course they’re pleased. $100,000 – what a dinky little fine. And Morgan Stanley is laughing all the way to the bank. These pathetic fines amount to corporate welfare and, of course, nobody ever goes to jail. If one of the 99 percenters broke the law can you imagine that they would be allowed to negotiate with the authorities on their sentence? NOT! Who would have thought that the justice system in the United States of America would have become so corrupt?
